## Create token for current user

```shell
$ curl 'https://ci.example.com/go/api/current_user/access_tokens' \
      -u 'username:password' \
      -H 'Accept: <%= data.apis.versions.access_token %>' \
      -X POST \
      -H 'Content-Type: application/json' \
      -d '{
        "description": "my first token"
      }'
```

> The above command returns JSON structured like this:

```http
HTTP/1.1 200 OK
Content-Type: <%= data.apis.versions.access_token %>; charset=utf-8
```

```json
{
  "_links" : {
    "self" : {
      "href" : "https://ci.example.com/go/api/current_user/access_tokens/42"
